joelib2.data
Class BasicAromaticityTyper

java.lang.Object
  joelib2.data.IdentifierSoftDefaultSystem
      joelib2.data.AbstractDataHolder
          joelib2.data.BasicAromaticityTyper
All Implemented Interfaces:
AromaticityTyper, IdentifierHardDependencies, IdentifierSoftDependencies
public class BasicAromaticityTyper
extends AbstractDataHolder
implements IdentifierHardDependencies, AromaticityTyper

Aromatic typer. The definition file can be defined in the joelib2.data.JOEAromaticTyper.resourceFile property in the BasicPropertyHolder. The BasicResourceLoader loads the joelib2.properties file for default.

Default:
joelib2.data.JOEAromaticTyper.resourceFile=joelib2/data/plain/aromatic.txt

See Also:
BasicPropertyHolder, BasicResourceLoader

assignAromaticFlags

public void assignAromaticFlags(Molecule mol,
                                AtomDynamicResult atoms,
                                BondDynamicResult bonds)
Assign the aromaticity flag to atoms and bonds. 3 rings will be excluded. Please remember that the aromaticity typer JOEAromaticTyper.assignAromaticFlags(Molecule) assign ONLY aromaticity flags and NOT the internal aromatic bond order Bond.JOE_AROMATIC_BOND_ORDER.

Specified by:
assignAromaticFlags in interface AromaticityTyper
Parameters:
mol - the molecule
